data.description: Desirable 2 story home in Tinley Park! 2 large bedrooms plus a great loft space and 2 newly renovated baths in this uniquely beautiful house with a great layout. You'll notice as you walk in, the spacious living room and sitting/dining area that lead to the adorable kitchen. From there step down to a very charming open eating area with a large bay window overlooking the nicely finished fenced in backyard. There is an oversized main floor master bedroom with plenty of room to relax with it's own private walk-out to the outdoor deck! Upstairs you'll love the large cozy loft with newer hardwood flooring, a warm inviting fireplace, a wet-bar and plenty of room for entertaining or office space. Could easily become a 3rd bedroom. The large second bedroom upstairs, recently updated, has plenty of closet space and large bright windows. There are wonderful skylights throughout this home that really let the light in. The backyard is beautiful with a new PVC fence surrounding and a huge double platform deck! Detached two car garage was recently painted and new garage door opener installed. The full basement has the potential to suit all your needs. The AC, Furnace and Water Heater all have been replaced in 2020! Newer vinyl siding, rear roof, skylights, windows and appliances. The sellers love the excellent location, within walking distance to the train and the popular downtown Tinley. I-80 is minutes away as well as excellent schools, restaurants and shopping. You must see this home to really appreciate...
